From: October 2022

Sal Y Pimienta Salt&Pepper Logo

Sal y Pimienta is a food truck business that is also launching an academy to teach local communities how to start their own food truck ventures. The client wanted the logo to resonate with Latino culture, so the design focused on typography, using a letter style that feels organic and dynamic. The letterforms were inspired by vintage posters, giving them a nostalgic yet fresh vibe. The overall look had to be friendly and inviting, so two characters were created—Salt and Pepper. These characters were designed in a simple line art style and later animated to bring them to life, further enhancing the brand's playful and approachable personality.
